30 SUMMARY
3311 This amendment reduces to 5 the number of income tax brackets proposed in the bill
3322 for each filing status, adjusts the tax brackets and increases the rate of tax on the top 2
3333 brackets to 7.75% and 8.95%, respectively. The amendment also adjusts the dates for
3344 indexing.
